== Exercise 3: Wire the risk classifier and approval gate into the supervisor

// TODO: Add full supervisor update for module-05 with risk classifier integration

Open `module-05-compliance/supervisor.py` and trace how it:

. Gets the Kira ticket
. Runs subagent investigations
. Generates a proposed remediation action
. Calls the risk classifier
. Routes based on risk level:
+
[source,python]
----
risk = classifier.classify(ticket, proposed_action)

if risk == RiskLevel.LOW:
    # Human out of the loop — act immediately
    remediate(ticket, proposed_action)
    log_compliance(ticket_id, proposed_action, "AUTO_REMEDIATED")

elif risk == RiskLevel.MEDIUM:
    # Human on the loop — act after 5-minute hold, notify channel
    notify_rocketchat(f"⏳ Acting in 5 min unless rejected: {proposed_action}")
    time.sleep(300)
    if not veto_received():
        remediate(ticket, proposed_action)
        log_compliance(ticket_id, proposed_action, "AUTO_REMEDIATED_NO_VETO")

elif risk == RiskLevel.HIGH:
    # Human in the loop — block until approved
    approved = approval_gate.request_approval(
        ticket_id, proposed_action, evidence, risk.value
    )
    if approved:
        remediate(ticket, proposed_action)
        log_compliance(ticket_id, proposed_action, "REMEDIATED_AFTER_APPROVAL")
    else:
        escalate(ticket_id, "Approval rejected or timed out")
        log_compliance(ticket_id, proposed_action, "ESCALATED")
----

. Run the full supervisor:
+
